team.description:
We are [GDGYYC](https://www.gdgyyc.com/), Calgary's Google Cloud Developer Group. We're here to Build What's Next and Transform Legacy with Google Cloud and Cloud Native technology.
DevFestYYC is bringing Alberta’s Startup and Enterprise developers, architects, data scientists and operations professionals together with world-class and top local speakers. We are also, Google Developers Group Cloud [Edmonton](https://gdgedmonton.com/). We're an official chapter of Google’s worldwide network of cloud enthusiasts, developers, data scientists and cloud engineers. Our goal is to become the largest community of developers in Edmonton, through various technology events, learning opportunities, and access to the latest Google products. We help our members to grow by advancing their skills, network and career. Find more about Cloud Edmonton [here](https://gdgedmonton.com/).

blocks.title: Organizer
blocks.description: GDGYYC and GDG Cloud Edmonton are the proud organizers of DevFestAB. We're here to build a world-class developer community in Alberta.

blocks.title: What is GDG?
blocks.description: Google Developers Groups (GDG) are the world's largest network of technologists. GDG chapters can be found in over 1000 cities around the world. GDGs are committed to advancing developer knowledge of Google Cloud and Cloud Native technologies.
